er one thing. There are some people on this yahoogroup, who are already qui=
te pure with just a few shortcomings that are blocking them. They have made=
 good progress in the last 3-4 years. In the years to come, some more peopl=
e will make a lot of progress. What is good enough for them may not be good=
 enough for most people.
 
