ome simple food and imagine the god in fire to be actually eating that food=
! External ritual is not an obstruction for visualization. In fact, it prov=
ides a platform for visualization. You can build whatever structures you wa=
nt, on top of that platform!
 
One can imagine that the deity is really sit=
ting in fire. One can imagine that the deity is being given a garland with =
several nice flowers. One can imagine that the deity is enjoying the incens=
e. One can imagine that the deity is enjoying nice foods. And so on.
 
